item.title: By: Judith
item.dc:creator: Judith
item.description: <p>Sounds like your having a great time and the county apartment looks lush, sadly Ipswich are now out of the play off's but after the atmosphere there last night thank goodness it was nasty we left 10mins early it was that bad! looking forward to seeing inside out house this weekend and seeing the family enjoy the rest of trip</p>
